<Layout>
	<!-- Раздел "Обо мне" -->
  <section id="about">
    <h3>About Me</h3>
    <p>Lead engineer and technical manager with 10+ years of experience. Currently, I lead the technology strategy at SuperStartup, where we develop AI-based cloud solutions. Previously, I worked at AcmeCorp and TechSolutions, where I launched several successful products.</p>
    <p>I actively share my knowledge: I speak at conferences and write a blog. I value minimalism in code and design, focusing on performance and user convenience.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Раздел "Проекты" -->
  <section id="projects">
    <h3>Projects and Achievements</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>SuperProduct X</strong> – development of a high-load platform (100k+ daily users).</li>
      <li><strong>OpenSource Library Y</strong> – created a popular library (5k stars on GitHub) for data processing.</li>
      <li><strong>Award Z</strong> – ranked in the top 10 young CTOs by TechMagazine (2024).</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Раздел "Контакты" -->
  <section id="contacts">
    <h3>Contacts</h3>
    <p>I would be glad to engage in professional communication and new projects. You can contact me via email or social media:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:ivan@example.com">ivan@example.com</a><br/>
       <strong>LinkedIn:</strong> <a href="#">ivan-ivanov</a><br/>
       <strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="#">@ivanivanov</a></p>
  </section>
</Layout>
